ivardefs.name: author
ivardefs.desc: Indicates who was responsible for creating the resource instance.

ivardefs.name: code
ivardefs.desc: Identifies the 'type' of resource - equivalent to the resource name for other resources.

ivardefs.name: created
ivardefs.desc: Identifies when the resource was first created.

ivardefs.name: identifier_
ivardefs.desc: Identifier assigned to the resource for business purposes, outside the context of FHIR.

ivardefs.name: subject
ivardefs.desc: Identifies the patient, practitioner, device or any other resource that is the "focus" of this resource.
